name: code_challenge
description: ## requirements for the project Was tasked to create a command line app that accomplished the following   *  This application should allow you to:   *  Type in a query and display a list of 5 books matching that query.   *  Each item in the list should include the book's author, title, and publishing company.   *  A user should be able to select a book from the five displayed to save to a “Reading List”   *  View a “Reading List” with all the books the user has selected from their queries -- this is a local reading list and not tied to Google Books’s account features.
